e="preserve">Anikó Gyöngyössy (born 21 May 1990) is a Hungarian water polo player. She's the goalkeeper for Budapesti VSC (BVSC) until 2022.
She played in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2010 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2019 World Aquatics Championships, 2020 Women's European Water Polo Championship.
